countless times from danger.)

59
00:04:30,259 --> 00:04:32,279
(Now, it's my turn to help you.)

60
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:37,819
Did Feng Changgeng tell you

61
00:04:38,579 --> 00:04:40,139
to use your blood to save Ye Chenyuan?

62
00:04:41,699 --> 00:04:42,860
You mustn't agree.

63
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,860
