67
00:05:57,920 --> 00:06:00,120
(the Night Deity's power
truly aids his recovery.)

68
00:06:01,459 --> 00:06:02,060
(Never mind.)

69
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:04,079
(As long as he can revive)

70
00:06:04,839 --> 00:06:05,879
(and return to me,)

71
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,439
(I'll pay any price.)

72
00:06:15,899 --> 00:06:17,480
