224
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:17,980
Take it easy.

225
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:19,220
Let's take it slow.

226
00:20:22,559 --> 00:20:23,680
This remote place

227
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:25,220
is free from disturbances.

228
00:20:27,172 --> 00:20:30,599
♪Borrowing a full moon from heaven♪

229
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:32,859
Only you and me.

230
00:20:37,119 --> 00:20:38,039
Just us two.

231
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:41,700
Inside here.

232
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:19,779
Why did you shield me earlier?

233
00:21:20,059 --> 00:21:21,220
I didn't want you hurt.

234
00:21:23,779 --> 00:21:24,339
Don't worry.

235
00:21:25,099 --> 00:21:26,420
I was merely caught off guard.

236
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:29,779
These enemies aren't worth fearing.

237
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,140
Are you okay?

238
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:00,799
Yes.

239
00:22:01,460 --> 00:22:02,740
Some rest will suffice.

240
00:22:04,940 --> 00:22:05,900
You protected me.

241
00:22:06,140 --> 00:22:06,940
It made me happy.

242
00:22:09,099 --> 00:22:09,900
Your joy

243
00:22:10,640 --> 00:22:11,500
brings me joy.

244
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,799
(Controlling so many puppets at once.)

245
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:19,579
(That familiar aura about them)

246
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:21,160
(and their familiar moves.)

247
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:22,880
(You fool)

248
00:22:23,359 --> 00:22:24,579
(shouldn't have done this.)

249
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:27,660
Xiaoying.

250
00:22:33,599 --> 00:22:34,759
I know it was you.

251
00:22:38,500 --> 00:22:39,799
