262
00:23:01,220 --> 00:23:02,660
wouldn't have been hurt by puppets.

263
00:23:03,900 --> 00:23:04,740
I haven't.

264
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:06,779
Ye Chenyuan's become a monster now.

265
00:23:07,180 --> 00:23:08,539
