00:23:44,859 --> 00:23:46,019
You can abandon everything

281
00:23:46,140 --> 00:23:47,460
for him.

282
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:49,380
If you listened to my words,

283
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:51,380
would I resort to
such desperate measures?

284
00:23:54,380 --> 00:23:57,660
(He doesn't respect you
like he respected the Immortal Lord.)

285
00:23:58,140 --> 00:23:58,779
Xiaoying.

286
00:23:58,779 --> 00:24:00,299
(You trust him as your right hand,)

287
00:24:00,579 --> 00:24:02,339
(but he defies your control.)

288
00:24:02,779 --> 00:24:04,740
(He'll break free from you)

289
00:24:05,019 --> 00:24:05,940
(and betray you.)

290
00:24:06,099 --> 00:24:06,660
Xiaoying.

291
00:24:07,140 --> 00:24:07,880
What's wrong?

292
00:24:14,019 --> 00:24:14,819
Yunya.

293
00:24:16,339 --> 00:24:17,940
You're too self-righteous.

294
00:24:20,059 --> 00:24:21,819
Always trying to change me

295
00:24:22,539 --> 00:24:24,220
instead of submitting to me.

296
00:24:24,799 --> 00:24:25,519
Xiaoying,

297
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:26,819
calm down.

298
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:28,279
Don't get influenced.

299
00:24:36,460 --> 00:24:38,460
You claim I neglect all matters,

300
00:24:40,019 --> 00:24:41,940
but I ordered you
to conquer the Three Realms,

301
00:24:42,319 --> 00:24:43,779
to uplift our clan's prestige.

302
00:24:44,779 --> 00:24:45,700
Have you done it?

303
00:24:46,059 --> 00:24:46,779
Xiaoying,

304
00:24:47,019 --> 00:24:47,500
I...

305
00:24:49,039 --> 00:24:50,880
You constantly oppose me.

306
00:24:51,140 --> 00:24:54,140
Do you think I'm still
that low-level disciple at your mercy?

307
00:24:59,099 --> 00:24:59,779
Fine!

308
00:25:01,339 --> 00:25:02,380
Since that's how it is,

309
00:25:04,059 --> 00:25:05,859
you'll regret

310
00:25:06,299 --> 00:25:07,460
your choices.

311
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:10,500
Xiaoying.

312
00:25:11,859 --> 00:25:12,859
Xiaoying.

313
00:25:16,940 --> 00:25:17,900
Issue my command!

314
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:20,180
Gather all warriors immediately

315
00:25:20,599 --> 00:25:21,799
for battle!

316
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:23,160
- Yes!
- Yes!

317
00:25:53,539 --> 00:25:54,180
No!

318
00:25:55,859 --> 00:25:56,420
Xiaoying!

319
00:25:57,059 --> 00:25:57,579
Don't!

320
00:25:57,660 --> 00:25:58,259
Xiaoying!

321
00:26:03,579 --> 00:26:06,099
Have you forgotten how they treated you?

322
00:26:08,900 --> 00:26:10,420
Only by killing them

323
00:26:12,619 --> 00:26:14,779
will your suffering end.

324
00:26:24,799 --> 00:26:25,720
Angry?

325
00:26:26,920 --> 00:26:27,880
Desperate?

326
00:26:30,279 --> 00:26:32,079
This is my power now.

327
00:26:32,519 --> 00:26:34,400
None can stop me

328
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:37,380
destroying what I wish to!

329
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:40,920
I'm no longer

330
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:43,880
the helpless Bai Xiaoying!

331
00:26:46,240 --> 00:26:46,920
No.

332
00:26:47,660 --> 00:26:48,339
Xiaoying.

333
00:26:49,539 --> 00:26:50,900
This isn't your true nature.

334
00:26:51,339 --> 00:26:52,660
The Night Deity controls you.

335
00:26:57,319 --> 00:26:59,200
Can't you see this?

336
00:27:02,759 --> 00:27:04,259
I am the Night Deity.

337
00:27:05,839 --> 00:27:06,839
The Night Deity

338
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,880
is me.

339
00:27:12,180 --> 00:27:15,146
(Falling Snow)

340
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:41,920
Lord.

341
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,319
Say it.

342
00:28:03,119 --> 00:28:05,240
All captives are in the prison,

343
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,440
