344
00:28:09,759 --> 00:28:10,480
Perfect.

345
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,119
Let's enjoy something amusing.

346
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:14,759
Come.

347
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,759
I come today

348
00:28:38,519 --> 00:28:40,920
to discuss a minor matter.

349
00:28:42,039 --> 00:28:43,680
As you all know,

350
00:28:44,359 --> 00:28:46,839
the Nine Heavens now
submit to the Night Clan.

351
00:28:48,119 --> 00:28:49,440
From today onward,

352
00:28:50,039 --> 00:28:51,960
if you pledge allegiance
to us and honor me

353
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:53,640
as your lord,

354
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:56,640
you may leave now.

355
00:28:57,940 --> 00:28:59,160
I agree! I agree!

356
00:28:59,519 --> 00:29:00,839
Please spare me.

357
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:01,720
And I'll return

358
00:29:01,880 --> 00:29:03,559
to destroy all immortal temples

359
00:29:03,759 --> 00:29:05,279
and worship only you!

360
00:29:07,140 --> 00:29:07,859
Good.

361
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,599
Swallow this pill,

362
00:29:14,160 --> 00:29:15,480
and obey henceforth.

363
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,720
- I'll take it!
- I'll take it!

364
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:26,480
This way.

365
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:35,400
We meet again.

366
00:29:37,119 --> 00:29:38,680
I never imagined you two

367
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,759
would end up like this.

368
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:42,039
Well?

369
00:29:42,660 --> 00:29:44,039
Must I take your pill too

370
00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:46,559
to gain freedom?

371
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:49,519
Your friendship was with Ye Chenyuan,

372
00:29:49,839 --> 00:29:50,559
not me.

373
00:29:51,359 --> 00:29:52,319
Unfortunately,

374
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,799
