375
00:30:02,599 --> 00:30:03,839
Why look at them?

376
00:30:04,759 --> 00:30:06,599
They can't even protect themselves.

377
00:30:06,839 --> 00:30:08,480
Expecting their rescue? How naive.

378
00:30:14,599 --> 00:30:15,279
Fine.

379
00:30:16,319 --> 00:30:17,000
I'll take it.

380
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,200
We take this pill

381
00:30:35,519 --> 00:30:36,519
and you'll let us go?

382
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:37,920
Exactly.

383
00:30:39,039 --> 00:30:39,599
Pah!

384
00:30:41,359 --> 00:30:42,119
Bai Xiaoying.

385
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,880
Don't think we all fear you.

386
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,039
Listen.

387
00:30:45,240 --> 00:30:46,319
We immortals would rather

388
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,660
die than submit!

389
00:30:47,660 --> 00:30:48,819
Kill me if you dare.

390
00:30:49,619 --> 00:30:50,380
Fine.

391
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:54,119
I'll grant your wish.

